<bibRefCitation author="Zhang, Y. L. &amp; Webb, M. D." box="[837,1052,1947,1971]" pageId="10" pageNumber="235" pagination="1 - 103" refId="ref11914" refString="Zhang, Y. L. &amp; Webb, M. D. (1996) A revised classification of the Asian and Pacific Selenocephalinae leafhoppers (Homoptera: Cicadellidae). Bulletin of the Natural History Museum, Entomology Series, 65, 1 - 103." type="journal article" year="1996">Zhang &amp; Webb 1996</bibRefCitation>
